high_descs: turn around, then turn right to face the sink
pick up the knife with the yellow handle
face the apple in the sink
cut the apple with the knife into four pieces
put the knife down on the counter top to the right of the sink
pick up a slice of apple from the sink
turn around and go to the opposite side of the room, then turn left to face the refrigerator
place the apple slice in the refrigerator on the second from the top shelf on the right, let it cool for a few seconds, then open the door and take it out
turn around to face the wooden table on the wall opposite the refrigerator
place the apple slice on the table between the two grey plates
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple in the sink and cool a slice of it down in the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn around, head toward the table and turn right to the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Move to the right and toward the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn around and head to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick the slice of apple back up.
Turn around and head to the table.
Put the slice of apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink on the right
Pick up the knife from the sink
Move to the right and go to the apple in the sink
Cut the apple into three pieces
Put the knife point side down to the right of the sink
Take the apple piece on the right
Turn right and head to the refrigerator
Put the apple piece on the second shelf of the refrigerator, close the door, then open the door and take in out
Turn around and go to the table
Put the apple piece on the table between the two gray plates
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled and cut apple on the table
